  <blockquote> <p>Competencies: Verbal communication, Self development- awareness of strengths and areas for development, pursuing and applying feedback, multi-tasking in a fast-paced environment, maintaining a successful personal brand while providing critical feedback,
        Professionalism - Being present and prepared, prioritizing and completing tasks to accomplish goals.</p> 
        <p>Students have a limited timeframe to develop an idea for a landscape scene and paint the scene with acrylic paint. The scene must incorporate depth creating visual choices. In a verbal critique, they present their idea to peers with a pencil sketch.  The class gives feedback. Students are encouraged to discuss successful choices as they complete painting in an open studio environment.</p></blockquote>



</worksheet>
